description:
Darkness Radio goes bananas on our Supernatural News/ParaShare Genesis of the Planet of the Apes Edition!

This week the boys face the harsh reality that the world may not end by Killer A.I. or Zombie infestation but instead by the Great Monkey Uprising! Plus Haunted Houses for Sale, Dan Aykroyd returns to paranormal TV programming, a NEW Holzer Files TV special on June 11 PLUS your real stories of strange supernatural encounters.
